    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban knives and increase minimum sentences for certain offences",
        "additional_details": "The answer is simple, ban knives & increase minimum sentences to 10 years for possession with intent and 20 years for using a knife, and a whole life sentence for taking a life.\r\n\r\nSo far nothing has really had any significant impact on deterring people from carrying or using a knife and we have to adopt a zero tolerance approach so anyone even considering carrying a knife knows they risk an automatic 10 years in prison just for possession with intent, 20 years for using a knife and a whole life sentence for taking a life. We see knife crime almost everyday, lives are taken too soon all the time and something has to be done. No more half measures or token gestures, Zero Tolerance.",
        "background": "We believe knife crime is out of control and current minimum sentences are token gestures and never going to change anything. ",
